<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Search Platforms - Digital Literacy Campaign</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="jobsearch.css">
</head>
<body>

   
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>How to Use Job Search Platforms</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your guide to finding and applying for jobs online</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    
    <section class="intro">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>
                Job search platforms have transformed how people find employment. 
                Whether you are a fresh graduate or an experienced professional, 
                online job portals like <strong>Naukri</strong>, <strong>Indeed</strong>, <strong>Apna</strong>, and 
                <strong>Mahajobs</strong> help connect you with recruiters and companies directly.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="platforms">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Popular Job Search Platforms in India</h2>
            <div class="platform-list">
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <img src="https://static.naukimg.com/s/4/100/i/naukri_Logo.png" alt="Naukri">
                    <h3>Naukri.com</h3>
                    <p>Create a resume, set up job alerts, and apply directly to employers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <img src="logo/indeed.png" alt="Indeed">
                    <h3>Indeed</h3>
                    <p>Search by job title, company, or location and apply instantly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <img src="logo/apna.jpg" alt="Apna">
                    <h3>Apna</h3>
                    <p>Specially designed for quick blue-collar and entry-level job searches.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-card">
                    <img src="logo/mahajobs.jpg" alt="Mahajobs">
                    <h3>Mahajobs</h3>
                    <p>Government initiative to connect job seekers with industries in Maharashtra.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="steps">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Step-by-Step Guide</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Choose a Job Portal:</strong> Select one or more platforms that fit your career goals.</li>
                <li><strong>Create an Account:</strong> Use your email or phone number to sign up.</li>
                <li><strong>Build Your Profile:</strong> Upload your resume, profile picture, and skills.</li>
                <li><strong>Search for Jobs:</strong> Use keywords and filters like location, experience, and salary.</li>
                <li><strong>Apply:</strong> Click “Apply” and send your profile to employers.</li>
                <li><strong>Track Applications:</strong> Keep checking for recruiter responses.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="tips">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Tips for Success</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Keep your profile updated regularly.</li>
                <li>Apply to multiple jobs every week.</li>
                <li>Use a professional photo and resume format.</li>
                <li>Respond to recruiter messages quickly.</li>
                <li>Be honest about your skills and experience.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

   
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>Digital Literacy Campaign | Helping people use digital tools effectively</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
